  Further review of dependencies.

  10 Mar 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  mate-session-manager-1.6.1-r1.ebuild:
  Remove invalid SLOT dependencies from pkg-config, gettext, intltool and xdg-
